---
name: Env Filter
version: 1.0.0
environments: [staging, production]
---

# Environment filtering

```step name="always-run"
echo "runs everywhere"
```

```step name="staging-only"
  env: [staging]
---
echo "staging only"
```

```step name="production-only"
  env: [production]
---
echo "production only"
```

```step name="also-always"
echo "also runs everywhere"
```
